宣布迄今为止<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-adds-four-extra-shows-to-2024-munich-residency-buy-tickets-3581367">在专门建造的慕尼黑展览中心举办了总共 10 场演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-announces-rescheduled-las-vegas-residency-dates-following-illness-3612322">阿黛尔因患病宣布重新安排拉斯维加斯驻场日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
